title: september 6: first ship to sail around the world
description:
In this episode of 365 days with mxmtoon, Maia talks about the treacherous journey of the first ship to sail all the way around the world. After, Maia revisits Elton John’s 1988 “garage sale” auctioning off over 2,000 of his personal belongings. Listen to this episode today and make sure you’re following along with the daily updates @365daysmxmtoon on all platforms.
